*texinfo-4.13-r2 (09 Aug 2015)

  09 Aug 2015; Robin H. Johnson <robbat2@gentoo.org>
  +files/texinfo-4.13-accentenc-test.patch, +files/texinfo-4.13-docbook.patch,
  +files/texinfo-4.13-texi2dvi-regexp-range.patch,
